  "taskTitle": "English Language Tutoring for Refugee Families",
  "taskDescription": "Help refugee families and individuals learn English for employment, education, and daily integration. This is an intensive tutoring program focusing on conversational English, job interview preparation, and professional communication skills. Suitable for learners at beginner to intermediate levels. Sessions can be conducted online or in-person at our Kyiv center.",
  
